{"product_id":"nurme-protective-vitamin-lip-balm-4-5g","title":"NURME Protective Vitamin Lip Balm 4,5g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith cocoa butter and vitamin E. Protects from the cold, wind and sun. Softens and moisturizes the lips and prevents chapping. Extremely long-lasting, truly gentle and with a pleasant fragrance.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBeeswax protects lips from harsh weather conditions and acts as an antiseptic, cocoa butter moisturises lips, vitamin E regenerates skin cells and avocado oil nourishes and revitalises damaged lips.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to lips.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVitamin lip balm is also great for little ones, so feel free to put it in your school and kindergarten kid’s pocket.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eCera Alba (Beeswax), Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin-E), Citrus Nobilis (Mandarin) Peel Oil, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil (and) Beta Carotene, Limonene*, Linalool*. \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Occurs naturally in essential oils.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915920052551,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-protective-vitamin-lip-balm-45g-257622.webp?v=1739897173","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/nurme-protective-vitamin-lip-balm-4-5g","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}